3. COMPONENTS OF KNOWLEDGE GRAPHS

| Component    | Description                            |
| ------------ | -------------------------------------- |
| Entity       | Real-world object or concept           |
| Relationship | Connection between entities            |
| Attribute    | Properties of entities                 |
| Ontology     | Schema defining concepts and relations |

---

4. STRUCTURE OF A KNOWLEDGE GRAPH

Example Structure:

```text
[Person] ---- works_at ----> [Company]
     |
   lives_in
     ↓
   [City]
```

Example:

```text
Alice → works_at → Google
Alice → lives_in → Hyderabad
```

